title: Poroshenko Claims Russia Destroys 'World Order' by Striking ISIL in Syria
text: According to the Ukrainian leader, the Russian Air Force’s operation in Syria against ISIL is leading to global instability. On the eve of Petro Poroshenko’s accusation, Damascus said that Russian jets have destroyed 40% of the terrorists’ infrastructure. ...
